上直播现场情况。据悉，员工们“围堵”夏一平，主要担心CEO“跑路”，并提出诸多核心诉求，包括公司将今年10月和11月的员工社保、医保和公积金缴齐，离职日给员工“N+1”的赔偿款等。 极越CEO夏一平被员工围堵 图据南方都市报 图据界面新闻 每经记者 孙桐桐 摄 背靠百度、吉利两大实力股东，极越怎么会没钱了？ 据红星资本局，知情人士告诉记者，百度与吉利对极越的前景并不看好，不再提供资金支持。今年上半年，极越与股东谈好了新一轮30亿元融资，原定于下半年到账，但百度突然不出了，这时候极越账上已经没钱了。 极越此次突然倒下，与股权变更和更名有关。2021年1月，百度与吉利共同成立集度汽车，百度持股55%，吉利持股45%。2022年6月，集度汽车发布了首款概念车ROBO-01。2023年8月，因生产资质问题，集度汽车更名为极越，吉利持股上升至65%。2023年10月底，极越首款量产车极越01正式上市。 最新！极越两大股东内部已开始转账流程，为其员工缴11月社保"},"attached_info":"CkEIx4CZ0t+Cw+USEAMaCTExMjMyMTk5NSD66+26BjAAOIsDQAFyCjY3MjY3MTA0Mjd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"1007 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-b719994d36c0a948e8ca08313841283d_1440w.jpeg?source=7e7ef6e2&needBackground=1"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"2_1734089086.85706","card_id":"Q_6685105144","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":6685105144,"title":"如何评价《再见爱人 4》第九期（下）？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/6685105144","type":"question","created":1734001913,"answer_count":29,"follower_count":39,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[982,4728,22839,3743562,3754367],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"习惯性盘它。"},"attached_info":"CkAIx4CZ0t+Cw+USEAMaCTExMjMxMzcwNyD5ieu6BjAAOCdAAnIKNjY4NTEwNTE0NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"159 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-80d6c1d97eb0f039ca7698d0d62c14ef_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"3_1734089086.86093","card_id":"Q_4995329934","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3